# ORIG TITLE    Siberian boffins positive about ‘youth pill’ . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Scientists in Siberia have reported positive results from tests they have made on themselves using so-called anti-ageing drugs. They decided to press ahead without waiting for official clinical trials which are due in November. It is believed the regenerative medication, which was originally developed to treat liver cirrhosis, will not be available for several years. 
